  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "I hate how you all say goodbye, goodbye One tried goodbye, always, always, always goodbye I can see the clouds lifting away From the thoughts that darkness interrupts my day There's no way to have it all anyway I pray that these choices have salvation And I pray that you let just a little light stab your heart Let just a little light stab your heart I know it's cold outside But you gotta keep moving on You gotta move on from here Move right here You gotta move on from here Move right in time The thoughts come alive again in time I feel this was not my time Don't treat me like this distance But let go this instance Goodbye But don't treat me like I'm just a one take moment Years lost in cold moments Years gone and I don't know if I can Find that breath Feeling the love again It's moved on All the light passes down It's moved on I move on I move on So alone I move on So alone And sometimes you'll find a way And sometimes you'll find a way back to To the people you knew To the things that you loved So lost and far again Don't know where you'll find a way back to",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 10.800000190734863,
      "text": "I hate how you all say goodbye, goodbye",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 22.65999984741211,
      "text": "One tried goodbye, always, always, always goodbye",
      "start": 12.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 27.559999465942383,
      "text": "I can see the clouds lifting away",
      "start": 23.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 32.41999816894531,
      "text": "From the thoughts that darkness interrupts my day",
      "start": 27.559999465942383
    },
    {
      "end": 38.65999984741211,
      "text": "There's no way to have it all anyway",
      "start": 32.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 46.400001525878906,
      "text": "I pray that these choices have salvation",
      "start": 40.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 58.20000076293945,
      "text": "And I pray that you let just a little light stab your heart",
      "start": 46.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 64.81999969482422,
      "text": "Let just a little light stab your heart",
      "start": 59.560001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 70.83999633789062,
      "text": "I know it's cold outside",
      "start": 66.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 74.83999633789062,
      "text": "But you gotta keep moving on",
      "start": 70.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 79.0199966430664,
      "text": "You gotta move on from here",
      "start": 75.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 83.76000213623047,
      "text": "Move right here",
      "start": 80.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 87.83999633789062,
      "text": "You gotta move on from here",
      "start": 83.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 96.27999877929688,
      "text": "Move right in time",
      "start": 90.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 102.4800033569336,
      "text": "The thoughts come alive again in time",
      "start": 97.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 109.86000061035156,
      "text": "I feel this was not my time",
      "start": 103.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 116.45999908447266,
      "text": "Don't treat me like this distance",
      "start": 111.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 120.58000183105469,
      "text": "But let go this instance",
      "start": 116.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 121.36000061035156,
      "text": "Goodbye",
      "start": 120.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 129.4199981689453,
      "text": "But don't treat me like I'm just a one take moment",
      "start": 122.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 132.97999572753906,
      "text": "Years lost in cold moments",
      "start": 129.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 139.13999938964844,
      "text": "Years gone and I don't know if I can",
      "start": 132.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 142.66000366210938,
      "text": "Find that breath",
      "start": 139.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 146.74000549316406,
      "text": "Feeling the love again",
      "start": 142.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 152.22000122070312,
      "text": "It's moved on",
      "start": 147.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 156.74000549316406,
      "text": "All the light passes down",
      "start": 152.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 163.47999572753906,
      "text": "It's moved on",
      "start": 157.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 166.75999450683594,
      "text": "I move on",
      "start": 163.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 169.74000549316406,
      "text": "I move on",
      "start": 166.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 172.55999755859375,
      "text": "So alone",
      "start": 170.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 176.6999969482422,
      "text": "I move on",
      "start": 172.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 204.60000610351562,
      "text": "So alone",
      "start": 202.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 214.1999969482422,
      "text": "And sometimes you'll find a way",
      "start": 211.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 220.02000427246094,
      "text": "And sometimes you'll find a way back to",
      "start": 215.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 223.74000549316406,
      "text": "To the people you knew",
